---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — HVAC Software Hub"
  description="Privacy Policy for HVAC Software Hub. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <section class="container py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      <div class="prose space-y-6">

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>HVAC Software Hub ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website hvacsoftwarehub.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website. Please read this policy carefully. If you disagree with its terms, please discontinue use of the site.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on pages, referring URLs, browser type, and device information, collected automatically via Google Analytics 4 (GA4).</li>
          <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> If you voluntarily subscribe to our email list or download a lead magnet, we collect your email address.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track activity on our site and hold certain information. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To analyze site traffic and improve content quality</li>
          <li>To send periodic emails if you have opted in to our mailing list</li>
          <li>To monitor and analyze usage patterns and trends</li>
          <li>To comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> Web analytics. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Affiliate Partners:</strong> When you click affiliate links, you are directed to third-party websites with their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their practices.</li>
          <li><strong>ConvertKit / Email Provider:</strong> If you subscribe to our email list, your email is stored with our email service provider.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">5. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>HVAC Software Hub participates in affiliate marketing programs. We earn commissions when you click certain links and make purchases. This does not affect the price you pay. See our full <a href="/disclosure" class="underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain analytics data as configured in Google Analytics (default: 14 months). Email subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe. We do not sell your personal data.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at the email below.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our site is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes are effective when posted on this page. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Meridian Gable Corp</strong><br />
        4000 S. Faber Place Drive, Suite 300<br />
        Charleston, SC 29405<br />
        Email: info@meridiangable.com</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
